      • builderTradeNo

        public PayCloseParamChain builderTradeNo(String tradeNo)
        !!This Is An Indispensable Parameter The Transaction In AliPay System Transaction Code. The Shortest 16 Bits, The Longest 64 Bits. And OutTradeNo Cannot Be Empty At The Same Time. If OutTradeNo And TradeNo Are Passed At The Same Time, TradeNo Shall Prevail.

        !!这是不可缺参数 该交易在支付宝系统中的交易流水号.最短 16 位,最长 64 位. 和OutTradeNo不能同时为空, 如果同时传了 OutTradeNo和 TradeNo, 则以 TradeNo为准.

        Parameters:
        tradeNo - tradeNo
